ru.myx.ae3.answer

Class Reply

  • Object
    • ru.myx.ae3.AbstractSAPI
      • ru.myx.ae3.answer.Reply

  • public class Reply
extends AbstractSAPI
    CD_XXX codes represent values of HTTP response codes, you can look up their values and descriptions online http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec10.html
    Author:
    barachta myx - barachta "typecomment": Window>Preferences>Java>Templates. To enable and disable the creation of type comments go to Window>Preferences>Java>Code Generation.
